ca certificates generated like Linux From Scratch

 http://www.linuxfromscratch.org/blfs/view/8.1/postlfs/cacerts.html

with this certdata

 http://anduin.linuxfromscratch.org/BLFS/other/certdata.txt

with this command

./make-ca.sh -D $PWD/output/

and moving ca-bundle.crt to certs/ca-certificates.crt

resulting certificates are reduced/reorganized into an archive in order to make Slackbuild more simpler.